				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\delta _{i}^{H}$\end{document}δiH, which distributes an individual’s force of infection across the resident populations of their home SA3 and other SA3s that they visit.

